<plot>Short film which chronicles the events of the Tulip Revolution in Kyrgyzstan. The author tries to assess the events of March 2005 in Kyrgyzstan and to go on living after the shock of what has happened. He must live with his bittersweet love for his small country all the while nourishing the hope that one day he will live to see it proud and strong.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?158061</url></doc>
